      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "When you pass toArray() an array of too small size, the toArray() method has to construct a new array of the right size using reflection. This has significantly worse performance than passing in an array of at least the size of the collection itself.    Therefore <code>[0]</code> should be replaced with <code>[myset.size()]</code> as in the accepted answer."
